refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolmcrypt_module_is_block_mode stringmode stringlib_dir
This function returns &true; if the mode outputs blocks of bytes or &false; if it outputs just bytes. (e.g. &true; for cbc and ecb, and &false; for cfb and stream).

&reftitle.parameters;




   mode

    &mcrypt.parameter.mode;



   lib_dir



     The optional lib_dir parameter can contain the
     location where the algorithm module is on the system.
